      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/2/22/79",
      "text": [
        " «ما انتفعت بكلام بعد كلام رسول الله (صلى الله عليه وآله) كانتفاعي بهذا الكلام»"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "To ‘Abdullāh ibn al-‘Abbās. ‘Abdullāh ibn al-‘Abbās used to say, ‘‘Apart from the Prophet’s sayings I did not derive greater benefit from any saying than this one.’’"
